@Aerolineas_HostAddress = http://localhost:5138
@authToken = # Pega aqu√≠ el token que obtengas del login

### 1. Registro de usuario
POST {{Aerolineas_HostAddress}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "admin@aerolinea.com",
    "password": "Admin123!",
    "nombre": "Administrador",
    "apellido": "Sistema"
}

### 2. Login para obtener token
POST {{Aerolineas_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "admin@aerolinea.com",
    "password": "Admin123!"
}

### 3. Obtener todas las aeronaves
GET {{Aerolineas_HostAddress}}/api/aeronaves
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 4. Crear nueva aeronave
POST {{Aerolineas_HostAddress}}/api/aeronaves
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "matricula": "XA-ABC",
    "modelo": "Boeing 737-800",
    "capacidad": 189,
    "anioFabricacion": 2020,
    "estadoOperativo": true
}

### 5. Obtener aeronave por ID
GET {{Aerolineas_HostAddress}}/api/aeronaves/1
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 6. Actualizar aeronave
PUT {{Aerolineas_HostAddress}}/api/aeronaves/1
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "modelo": "Boeing 737-800 Updated",
    "capacidad": 180,
    "estadoOperativo": true
}

### 7. Eliminar aeronave
DELETE {{Aerolineas_HostAddress}}/api/aeronaves/1
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
